I KNOW I WON!

00:03:28.535 --> 00:03:31.238
I SUMMONED GEARFRIED
THE IRON NIGHT
AND CRUSHED HIM!

00:03:31.238 --> 00:03:33.740
PLEASE, JOEY!
JUST LISTEN!

00:03:33.740 --> 00:03:36.209
YOU GUYS WERE PLAYING
A SHADOW GAME.

00:03:36.209 --> 00:03:38.245
AND YOU ALMOST WON,

00:03:38.245 --> 00:03:40.781
