BY DRAINING YOUR ENERGY.

00:03:42.682 --> 00:03:44.885
BUT THEN, WITH YOUR
LAST BIT OF STRENGTH

00:03:44.885 --> 00:03:47.087
YOU WERE ABLE
TO SUMMON A MONSTER

