STRONG ENOUGH
TO BEAT MARIK.

00:03:49.656 --> 00:03:52.392
BUT BEFORE YOU HAD
A CHANCE TO CALL OUT
YOUR ATTACK,

00:03:52.392 --> 00:03:59.433
YOU PASSED OUT.

00:03:59.433 --> 00:04:04.938
I DON T BELIEVE DIS.
DAT PSYCHO ACTUALLY
BEAT ME?

