THAN EITHER OF
YOUR CREATURES!

00:04:41.107 --> 00:04:45.078
NOW I'LL PLACE
TWO CARDS FACEDOWN!

00:04:45.078 --> 00:04:46.580
YOUR MOVE, YUGI.

