00:04:49.115 --> 00:04:51.117
YUGI WILL NEVER ESCAPE!

00:04:51.117 --> 00:04:54.688
KAIBA'S DEFINITELY UP
TO SOMETHING. BUT WHAT!?

00:04:54.688 --> 00:04:57.791
WE'VE GOT A LONG WAY
TO GO, KAIBA!

00:04:57.791 --> 00:05:00.760
THIS MAGIC CARD COULD
COME IN HANDY LATER,
BUT FOR NOW

00:05:00.760 --> 00:05:03.663
I HAVE HIS TWO BLUE-EYES
WHITE DRAGONS
TO WORRY ABOUT!

00:05:03.663 --> 00:05:05.665
