SOME SERIOUS DAMAGE

00:05:05.665 --> 00:05:08.735
SO I HAVE TO PROTECT
MY LIFE POINTS!

00:05:08.735 --> 00:05:11.137
I'LL PLACE THIS
FACEDOWN.

