00:05:17.544 --> 00:05:20.747
I ACTIVATE MY TRAP CARD!

00:05:20.747 --> 00:05:23.383
NO! NOT THAT TRAP!

00:05:23.383 --> 00:05:26.486
IT RETURNS
MY RED-EYES BACK
TO ATTACK MODE!

00:05:26.486 --> 00:05:28.154
IT'S WORSE THAN THAT!

00:05:28.154 --> 00:05:31.658
AS LONG AS MY FINAL ATTACK
ORDERS TRAP CARD IS IN PLAY,

00:05:31.658 --> 00:05:34.528
EVERY MONSTER ON THE FIELD
STAYS IN ATTACK MODE!

00:05:34.528 --> 00:05:37.531
AND NEXT, WE EACH CHOOSE
ANY THREE CARDS WE WANT

00:05:37.531 --> 00:05:39.466
IN ORDER TO FORM A NEW DECK

00:05:39.466 --> 00:05:42.469
AND THE REST OF OUR DECK GOES
TO THE CARD GRAVEYARD!

00:05:42.469 --> 00:05:45.138
OUR WHOLE DECK!?

00:05:45.138 --> 00:05:49.609
THAT MEANS THIS DUEL
COMES TO AN END
IN THREE MORE TURNS!

00:05:49.609 --> 00:05:53.647
THESE THREE CARDS
ARE MORE THAN ENOUGH
TO ENSURE MY VICTORY!

00:05:53.647 --> 00:05:56.316
IN A FEW SHORT MOMENTS
I'LL CRUSH YUGI

00:05:56.316 --> 00:05:58.785
AND RECLAIM
MY NUMBER ONE STATUS!

00:05:58.785 --> 00:06:00.253
NOW THEN

00:06:00.253 --> 00:06:04.090
YOU MAY AS WELL GIVE UP
AND ACCEPT DEFEAT NOW, YUGI,

00:06:04.090 --> 00:06:07.394
