GOES AWAY!

00:06:12.265 --> 00:06:15.268
MY FATE DEPENDS
ON THIS CHOICE!

00:06:19.501 --> 00:06:21.636
WHERE IS YUGI?
DID HIS DUEL START YET!?

00:06:21.636 --> 00:06:23.939
