AGAINST KAIBA RIGHT NOW!

00:06:23.939 --> 00:06:27.509
WHAT?! WELL DEN I GOTTA GET
UP THERE AND HELP HIM OUT!

00:06:27.509 --> 00:06:29.111
DON'T, JOEY!

00:06:29.111 --> 00:06:32.447
