TA TALK ME OUT OF IT.
HE NEEDS ME!

00:06:32.447 --> 00:06:33.882
JOEY, WAIT!

00:06:33.882 --> 00:06:36.118
HEY! GET BACK IN BED,
RIGHT NOW!

00:06:36.118 --> 00:06:40.155
KAIBA CORP EMERGENCY SQUAD!

00:06:40.155 --> 00:06:42.758
