AN EXAMINATION!

00:07:02.244 --> 00:07:04.012
MAYBE LATER.

00:07:04.012 --> 00:07:05.514
COME ON, YOU GUYS!

00:07:05.514 --> 00:07:06.515
HEY!

00:07:06.515 --> 00:07:08.116
DON'T GO!

00:07:08.116 --> 00:07:10.185
HUH?

00:07:10.185 --> 00:07:12.587
JOEY, YOU SHOULD
STAY BACK HERE.

00:07:12.587 --> 00:07:15.123
PLEASE JUST LISTEN
TO WHAT THE DOCTOR
SAYS.

00:07:15.123 --> 00:07:18.593
