CAN'T YA SEE I'M ALL RIGHT NOW?

00:07:18.593 --> 00:07:20.195
NO, YOU'RE NOT!

00:07:20.195 --> 00:07:22.497
YOU WERE JUST
IN REALLY BAD
SHAPE, JOEY!

00:07:22.497 --> 00:07:24.933
