HAVE BEEN HURT

00:07:31.139 --> 00:07:33.308
BECAUSE OF
THIS TOURNAMENT,
THAT'S ALL.

00:07:33.308 --> 00:07:36.845
TRUST ME. I KNOW.

00:07:36.845 --> 00:07:39.214
BUT I HAVE TO GO
AND BE THERE FOR YUGI!

00:07:39.214 --> 00:07:40.849
SORRY, GUYS!

00:07:40.849 --> 00:07:42.651
BUT, JOEY!

00:07:42.651 --> 00:07:44.586
LOOK, I KNOW I HAD YA
ALL SCARED

