DROPPED OFF AT THE ORPHANAGE

00:11:58.032 --> 00:12:01.202
AS A CHILD, I'VE HAD
TO FEND FOR MYSELF!

00:12:01.202 --> 00:12:04.205
I HAD TO TOUGHEN UP
TO PROTECT MOKUBA.

00:12:04.205 --> 00:12:08.776
THEN WE WERE ADOPTED
BY A TYRANT KNOWN
AS GOZABURO KAIBA!

00:12:08.776 --> 00:12:12.146
HE TAUGHT ME TO CRUSH
MY ENEMIES AND TRUST NO ONE,

00:12:12.146 --> 00:12:14.716
BUT NOTHING I EVER DID
SATISFIED HIM!

00:12:14.716 --> 00:12:18.252
SO USING THE RUTHLESS BUSINESS
TECHNIQUES HE TAUGHT ME,

00:12:18.252 --> 00:12:21.456
I OUTSMARTED HIM
AND TOOK OVER HIS COMPANY!

00:12:21.456 --> 00:12:24.959
NOW KAIBA CORP BELONGS TO ME!

00:12:24.959 --> 00:12:27.362
AND HE'S LONG GONE.

00:12:27.362 --> 00:12:29.564
BUT THAT'S STILL
NOT GOOD ENOUGH FOR ME!

00:12:29.564 --> 00:12:32.567
THERE'S ONE CONQUEST
I NEED TO FULFILL!

00:12:32.567 --> 00:12:34.769
AND THAT'S WHERE
YOU COME IN, YUGI!

00:12:34.769 --> 00:12:38.239
SO LISTEN! I'M THE BEST
AT EVERYTHING THAT I DO!

00:12:38.239 --> 00:12:42.443
BUT WHEN IT COMES TO BEING
THE BEST AT DUEL MONSTERS
YOU ARE IN MY WAY!

00:12:42.443 --> 00:12:46.748
SO ONCE I BEAT YOU
I CAN FORGET THE PAST FOR GOOD!

00:12:46.748 --> 00:12:51.085
THAT'S WHY I'M HERE!

00:12:51.085 --> 00:12:55.490
I NEVER KNEW SETO FELT
SO STRONGLY ABOUT OUR PAST.

00:12:55.490 --> 00:12:58.326
I KNOW THINGS WEREN'T EASY
BACK THEN,

00:12:58.326 --> 00:13:00.395
BUT WE DID HAVE EACH OTHER.

00:13:00.395 --> 00:13:02.730
I GUESS THAT WASN'T
GOOD ENOUGH FOR HIM.

00:13:02.730 --> 00:13:04.766
HE WANTS TO FORGET
EVERYTHING,

00:13:04.766 --> 00:13:06.968
INCLUDING THE PERSON
HE USED TO BE.

00:13:06.968 --> 00:13:11.372
BUT I LIKED SETO BACK THEN.
HE ACTUALLY USED TO SMILE.

00:13:11.372 --> 00:13:14.409
NOW HE WANTS TO GET RID
OF THAT SMILE FOREVER!

00:13:14.409 --> 00:13:17.345
SETO NEEDS TO REALIZE
THAT REACHING THE TOP

00:13:17.345 --> 00:13:19.414
DOESN'T HAVE TO MEAN
BEING MISERABLE!

00:13:19.414 --> 00:13:22.917
FACE IT, YUGI,
YOUR REIGN IS OVER!

00:13:22.917 --> 00:13:25.053
YOU NEVER CEASE
TO AMAZE ME.

00:13:25.053 --> 00:13:26.421
[CHUCKLING]

00:13:26.421 --> 00:13:27.889
WHY?

00:13:27.889 --> 00:13:31.159
ARE YOU ASTOUNDED BY
MY SUPERIOR DUELING
SKILLS, YUGI?

00:13:31.159 --> 00:13:32.427
NOT QUITE!

00:13:32.427 --> 00:13:33.861
IT'S YOUR COMPLETE
STUBBORNNESS

00:13:33.861 --> 00:13:37.198
AND YOUR LUST
FOR POWER THAT I FIND
SO PUZZLING, KAIBA!

00:13:37.198 --> 00:13:38.733
WHY'S THAT?

00:13:38.733 --> 00:13:41.302
IT HOLDS YOU BACK!
THAT'S WHY!

00:13:41.302 --> 00:13:42.637
YOU'LL NEVER DEFEAT ME

00:13:42.637 --> 00:13:44.939
WITH A HEART FULL
OF HATRED AND MISTRUST!

00:13:44.939 --> 00:13:47.508
HA! YOU'RE JUST TRYING
TO DISTRACT ME

00:13:47.508 --> 00:13:49.477
BECAUSE YOU'RE SCARED
OF LOSING!

00:13:49.477 --> 00:13:52.146
WHY DON'T I LET
MY ACTIONS SPEAK FOR ME?

00:13:52.146 --> 00:13:54.348
REVEAL FACEDOWN CARD!

00:13:54.348 --> 00:13:56.517
MY DOUBLE SPELL
MAGIC CARD!

00:13:56.517 --> 00:13:59.020
OH NO! NOT DOUBLE SPELL!

00:13:59.020 --> 00:14:00.088
THAT'S RIGHT!

00:14:00.088 --> 00:14:01.756
THIS CARD DUPLICATES
THE EFFECTS

00:14:01.756 --> 00:14:05.226
OF EVERY MAGIC CARD
YOU USED ON YOUR
LAST TURN, KAIBA!

00:14:05.226 --> 00:14:08.663
THAT INCLUDES
MONSTER REBORN
AND POLYMERIZATION!

00:14:08.663 --> 00:14:13.167
SO FIRST I'LL BRING
BUSTER BLADER BACK
FROM THE GRAVEYARD!

00:14:13.167 --> 00:14:15.536
NOW I'LL USE
POLYMERIZATION!

00:14:15.536 --> 00:14:22.143
FUSING MY DARK MAGICIAN
WITH MY BUSTER BLADER!!!

00:14:22.143 --> 00:14:26.314
FUSE WHATEVER YOU WANT,
MY ULTIMATE DRAGON IS
STILL STRONGER!

00:14:26.314 --> 00:14:29.450
YOUR MAGIC CARD
DIDN'T HELP YOU AT ALL!

00:14:29.450 --> 00:14:30.952
YOU'RE WRONG, KAIBA!

00:14:30.952 --> 00:14:32.887
FOR MY NEW
FUSION MONSTER
CARRIES WITH IT

00:14:32.887 --> 00:14:35.656
EVERY ONE
OF BUSTER BLADER'S
SPECIAL ABILITIES!

00:14:35.656 --> 00:14:37.925
THAT MEANS
ITS ATTACK STRENGTH
INCREASES

00:14:37.925 --> 00:14:41.095
BY 500 POINTS
FOR EVERY DRAGON
ON THE FIELD!

00:14:41.095 --> 00:14:44.265
THAT INCLUDES
YOUR BLUE-EYES
ULTIMATE DRAGON

00:14:44.265 --> 00:14:46.534
AS WELL AS MY
RED-EYES BLACK DRAGON!

00:14:46.534 --> 00:14:49.470
NOW BEHOLD THE POWER
OF DARK PALADIN

00:14:49.470 --> 00:14:52.473
THE ULTIMATE
MAGICAL SWORDSMAN!

00:15:00.281 --> 00:15:03.951
HA. GOOD MOVE, YUGI,
BUT NOT GOOD ENOUGH.

00:15:03.951 --> 00:15:05.820
SORRY. LOOK CLOSER!

00:15:05.820 --> 00:15:07.555
WHAT'S YOUR POINT,
KAIBA?

00:15:07.555 --> 00:15:09.824
YOUR MONSTER
MAY BE POWERFUL

00:15:09.824 --> 00:15:12.994
BUT IT'S STILL
600 ATTACK POINTS
WEAKER THAN MINE!

00:15:12.994 --> 00:15:16.130
WE SHALL SEE! MY MOVE!

00:15:16.130 --> 00:15:19.700
ALL RIGHT, I'M
DEPENDING ON THIS CARD
TO WIN THE DUEL!

00:15:19.700 --> 00:15:22.236
I HOPE IT WORKS.
'CAUSE AT THIS POINT,

00:15:22.236 --> 00:15:24.972
IT'S MY ONLY CHANCE
FOR VICTORY!

00:15:24.972 --> 00:15:28.910
I'LL PLACE ONE CARD
FACEDOWN AND END
MY TURN!

00:15:28.910 --> 00:15:32.146
THIS IS WHERE
IT ALL ENDS, YUGI!

00:15:32.146 --> 00:15:34.482
HA HA HA HA!

00:15:34.482 --> 00:15:37.685
NOW THEN, IT'S TIME TO PUT
AN END TO MY PAST FOR GOOD!

00:15:37.685 --> 00:15:41.122
AS SOON AS I WIN THIS
I CAN FINALLY MOVE ON!

00:15:41.122 --> 00:15:42.590
HOW FOOLISH!

00:15:42.590 --> 00:15:45.126
IT'S OUR PAST
THAT MAKES US
WHO WE ARE TODAY!

00:15:45.126 --> 00:15:46.494
WHATEVER.

00:15:46.494 --> 00:15:48.729
YOU MUST REMEMBER
WHAT HAPPENED BEFORE

00:15:48.729 --> 00:15:51.199
SO YOU CAN LEARN
FROM YOUR PAST.

00:15:51.199 --> 00:15:53.401
YOU CAN'T IGNORE
WHERE YOU CAME FROM.

00:15:53.401 --> 00:15:55.670
DON'T YOU KNOW
IT'S OUR HISTORY

00:15:55.670 --> 00:15:57.972
THAT SHAPES
OUR FUTURE, KAIBA!

00:15:57.972 --> 00:16:00.041
SAVE IT, YUGI!

00:16:00.041 --> 00:16:02.777
IT'S TIME TO MOVE ON,
NOT LOOK BACK!

00:16:02.777 --> 00:16:04.579
THE PAST IS OVER!

00:16:04.579 --> 00:16:07.949
AND NOTHING YOU SAY
WILL CHANGE MY MIND, YUGI!

00:16:07.949 --> 00:16:10.251
I NEED TO TAKE YOU
DOWN, NOW!

00:16:10.251 --> 00:16:13.254
ONLY THEN WILL I ATTAIN
TRUE GREATNESS!

00:16:19.018 --> 00:16:20.520
Yugi: YOUR DUEL TOWER
STANDS HERE

00:16:20.520 --> 00:16:23.323
SURROUNDED BY RUBBLE
AND DESTRUCTION.

00:16:23.323 --> 00:16:25.525
AND TO ME IT REPRESENTS
YOUR HEART.

00:16:25.525 --> 00:16:28.728
A STRONG OBJECT
SURROUNDED BY ANGER
AND HATRED.

00:16:28.728 --> 00:16:30.930
AND AS LONG
AS YOU'RE FUELED BY HATE

00:16:30.930 --> 00:16:33.199
YOU CAN NEVER
DEFEAT ME, KAIBA!

00:16:33.199 --> 00:16:37.403
DON'T YOU REALIZE MY INNER RAGE
PUSHES ME FORWARD!?

00:16:37.403 --> 00:16:39.439
AND THAT'S WHAT I'LL USE
TO CRUSH YOU!

00:16:39.439 --> 00:16:41.407
IF THAT'S THE CASE
THEN GO AHEAD

00:16:41.407 --> 00:16:43.643
AND DIRECT ALL
OF YOUR HATRED
TOWARDS ME.

00:16:43.643 --> 00:16:46.079
AND STRIKE ME DOWN
WITH YOUR RAGE!

00:16:46.079 --> 00:16:47.714
VERY WELL.

00:16:47.714 --> 00:16:51.885
BUT I ASSURE YOU
YOU WILL LIVE TO REGRET
THOSE WORDS, YUGI!

00:16:51.885 --> 00:16:55.255
BLUE-EYES ULTIMATE DRAGON
PREPARE FOR ATTACK!

00:16:55.255 --> 00:16:56.756
THIS IS IT.

00:16:56.756 --> 00:16:59.959
IF I DON'T STOP
HIS DRAGON'S ATTACK,
THIS DUEL IS OVER!

00:16:59.959 --> 00:17:03.096
I HAFTA BELIEVE
IN MY FRIENDS
AND TRUST IN MYSELF.

00:17:03.096 --> 00:17:08.601
IF I TRULY AM DESTINED
TO FACE MARIK...

00:17:08.601 --> 00:17:10.870
THEN THERE'S NO WAY
KAIBA WILL WIN THIS!

00:17:10.870 --> 00:17:12.538
MY FAITH IN THE HEART
OF THE CARDS

00:17:12.538 --> 00:17:15.108
WILL OVERPOWER
HIS HATRED ANY DAY!

00:17:15.108 --> 00:17:17.510
NOTHING CAN STAND
IN THE WAY OF
MY DESTINY!

00:17:17.510 --> 00:17:24.717
NOW MY DRAGON ATTACK!!!

00:17:24.717 --> 00:17:28.421
NOW I ACTIVATE
THE FACEDOWN CARD,
MAGIC FORMULA!

00:17:28.421 --> 00:17:30.156
HOW PATHETIC!

00:17:30.156 --> 00:17:33.726
I ACTIVATE ABSORB SPELL!

00:17:33.726 --> 00:17:37.463
THIS MAGIC CARD WILL ABSORB
THE POWER OF MAGIC FORMULA!

00:17:37.463 --> 00:17:41.968
THEREFORE THE ATTACK POINTS
YOU JUST ADDED TO
YOUR DARK PALADIN

00:17:41.968 --> 00:17:45.538
WILL BE TRANSFERRED
TO MY ULTIMATE DRAGON!

00:17:45.538 --> 00:17:49.375
HIS BLUE-EYES
ULTIMATE DRAGON IS
COMPLETELY UNSTOPPABLE!

00:17:49.375 --> 00:17:51.144
HA HA HA HA!

00:17:51.144 --> 00:17:54.914
NOW YOU'RE HISTORY!
ALONG WITH YOUR RED-EYES!

00:17:54.914 --> 00:17:57.884
AND DARK PALADIN
THE ULTIMATE MAGICAL SWORDSMAN!

00:17:57.884 --> 00:18:02.588
FAREWELL!

00:18:02.588 --> 00:18:04.891
[CHUCKLING]
IT'S OVER!

00:18:04.891 --> 00:18:07.593
YEAH!

00:18:07.593 --> 00:18:09.963
Tea: YUGI!

00:18:09.963 --> 00:18:11.731
THIS DOESN'T
LOOK GOOD!

00:18:11.731 --> 00:18:15.268
YUGI!

00:18:15.268 --> 00:18:16.836
I WIN!

00:18:16.836 --> 00:18:19.072
Yugi: I WOULDN'T BE
SO SURE OF THAT.

00:18:19.072 --> 00:18:22.608
REMEMBER, I STILL HAVE
ONE FACEDOWN CARD LEFT!

00:18:22.608 --> 00:18:24.477
KAIBA, YOU'RE DONE!

00:18:24.477 --> 00:18:25.979
YOU LIE!

00:18:25.979 --> 00:18:28.047
AS YOU WILL SOON SEE

00:18:28.047 --> 00:18:31.217
I'VE BEEN DESTINED
TO DEFEAT YOU
FOR 5,000 YEARS!

00:18:31.217 --> 00:18:32.518
ENOUGH!

00:18:32.518 --> 00:18:35.722
MY BLUE-EYES ULTIMATE DRAGON
CANNOT BE STOPPED, YUGI!!

00:18:35.722 --> 00:18:37.557
I'M AFRAID YOU'RE WRONG.

00:18:37.557 --> 00:18:39.926
BUT I'LL LET MY CARD
SPEAK FOR ITSELF!

00:18:39.926 --> 00:18:41.995
SO I PLAY THIS!

00:18:41.995 --> 00:18:46.933
MY DE-FUSION CARD!

00:18:46.933 --> 00:18:48.568
THIS MAGIC CARD
SPLITS UP

00:18:48.568 --> 00:18:50.470
YOUR BLUE-EYES
ULTIMATE DRAGON

00:18:50.470 --> 00:18:53.606
INTO THE THREE
ORIGINAL DRAGONS
YOU FUSED TO FORM IT,

00:18:53.606 --> 00:18:56.342
THUS STOPPING
YOUR ATTACK!

00:19:01.714 --> 00:19:05.551
NO! I NEED MY ULTIMATE DRAGON
TO WIN THE DUEL!

00:19:05.551 --> 00:19:10.523
THIS CAN'T BE HAPPENING!

00:19:10.523 --> 00:19:12.158
NOW, KAIBA,

00:19:12.158 --> 00:19:15.428
YOU HAVE THREE DRAGONS
ON THE FIELD
INSTEAD OF ONE!

00:19:15.428 --> 00:19:17.663
AND SINCE MY DARK
PALADIN RECEIVES

00:19:17.663 --> 00:19:20.099
500 ATTACK POINTS
FOR EVERY DRAGON
ON THE FIELD

00:19:20.099 --> 00:19:22.735
HE'S NOW THE STRONGEST
MONSTER IN PLAY!

00:19:22.735 --> 00:19:25.038
NOW, IT'S TIME
FOR MY FINAL MOVE!

00:19:25.038 --> 00:19:26.406
JUST GO!

00:19:26.406 --> 00:19:30.043
WITH PLEASURE, KAIBA!
ALL RIGHT.

00:19:30.043 --> 00:19:32.311
THE CARD IN MY HAND
WILL CONQUER
THE DARKNESS

00:19:32.311 --> 00:19:34.147
THAT NOW SURROUNDS
YOUR HEART!

00:19:34.147 --> 00:19:36.783
SO I PLAY
MY FINAL MAGIC CARD!

00:19:36.783 --> 00:19:39.085
DIFFUSION WAVE-MOTION!

00:19:39.085 --> 00:19:41.054
YOU'RE FINISHED!

00:19:41.054 --> 00:19:43.856
ALL I HAVE TO DO
IS GIVE UP 1,000
LIFE POINTS,

00:19:43.856 --> 00:19:45.591
AND THIS MAGIC CARD
WILL ENHANCE

00:19:45.591 --> 00:19:48.728
THE ATTACKING
CAPABILITIES OF
MY DARK PALADIN!

00:19:48.728 --> 00:19:50.430
NOW MY MONSTER
CAN ATTACK

00:19:50.430 --> 00:19:53.266
ALL THREE
OF YOUR BLUE-EYES
WHITE DRAGONS AT ONCE!

00:19:53.266 --> 00:19:55.568
HIS DARK PALADIN HAS
ENOUGH POWER

00:19:55.568 --> 00:19:58.504
TO WIPE OUT MY DRAGONS
AND MY LIFE POINTS!

00:19:58.504 --> 00:20:06.279
THIS DUEL IS OVER!

00:20:06.279 --> 00:20:10.650
YUGI! I WILL NOT BE DEFEATED
AT MY OWN TOURNAMENT!

00:20:10.650 --> 00:20:12.718
KAIBA, YOU'RE TOO LATE.

00:20:12.718 --> 00:20:15.721
DARK PALADIN, ATTACK!

00:20:21.961 --> 00:20:23.963
[GROANING]

00:20:31.971 --> 00:20:35.975
YOU LOSE, KAIBA!

00:20:35.975 --> 00:20:38.144
[ALL CHUCKLING]

00:20:38.144 --> 00:20:42.949
I TOLD YOU YOUR HATRED
AND YOUR LUST FOR POWER
WOULD NEVER PREVAIL!!

00:20:42.949 --> 00:20:44.851
I DID IT!

00:20:44.851 --> 00:20:47.086
BUT MY TOUGHEST BATTLE
IS STILL AHEAD

00:20:47.086 --> 00:20:49.655
WHEN I FACE MARIK
IN THE FINAL DUEL!

